        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "I already own this dress in red, but I'm considering purchasing the blue variation as well. It's such a versatile piece. I wonder if it comes in other colors too. 「このワンピース、赤は持ってるんだけど、色違いの青も買おうか迷ってるんだ。すごく着回しがきくからね。他に色があるか気になるな。」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "The car model is available in several color variations. Which one do you think suits it best? I'm deciding between the silver and the deep blue.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "The toy set included small figures in various color variations, which was a nice surprise for the kids. Each one was uniquely colored. It made playtime more interesting.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "しかしこういう見立てのようなことはもちろん見る人によっていろいろちがいうるものであり、なんら絶対普遍的価値のないものである。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "連句雑俎",
                "author": "寺田寅彦",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "それはほんとうのお仕着せなんかじゃなく、いろいろちがいがあるんですけれど、それでもともかく服を見ただけで城からやってきた従僕だって見わけがつくんです。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "城",
                "author": "DAS SCHLOSS",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
