          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "I absolutely loved these socks, so I ended up buying them in three different colors! They're so comfortable and versatile. I can wear a different color each day of the week.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "When I find a skirt I really like, I tend to buy it in multiple colors. It's such a useful item for my wardrobe. This way, I can create different outfits with ease.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "For the twins, I bought them the same model of backpack but in different colors. It's a fun way to differentiate their belongings. They were both very happy with their new, colorful backpacks.",
